This paper deals with emotion detection in text, which is a task in natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a tailored model using neural networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves text classification, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
